  "The Flesh Tearers are a successor Chapter of the Blood Angels constantly on the verge of succumbing to the bloodthirsty psychic curse known as the Black Rage.",
  "The Red Corsairs are a powerful warband of Chaos renegades, once Astral Claws, who dominate the infamous pirate haven known as the Maelstrom.",
