  "The Iron Warriors frequently employ terrifying Obliterators as their shock troops to breach the strongest fortifications.",
  "The Plague Marines of the Death Guard are so resilient due to Nurgle's \"blessings\" that they often continue fighting with horrific injuries that would kill a normal marine.",
