  "The Snotlings are the smallest and weakest Orkoids, primarily used by Orks as pets, target practice, or highly expendable ammunition.",
  "Ork Mekboyz are the mad scientists who maintain and invent all the ramshackle, yet functional, Ork technology.",
  "The Squigs are various forms of low-intelligence Orkoid fauna used for everything from food to attack animals and even crude musical instruments.",
