  "Rak'Gol are brutal, cybernetic-enhanced raiders who terrorize the fringes of the galaxy and possess a disturbing mastery of flesh-metal surgery.",
  "The Demiurg are a stout, asteroid-dwelling Xenos race known for their unparalleled skills in deep-space mining and engineering.",
  "The Nicassar are a peaceful, bear-like Xenos species with powerful telekinetic abilities, acting as merchant partners for the T'au Empire.",
  "The Laer were an ancient, serpent-like species who possessed a sacred artifact that corrupted the Primarch Fulgrim to the worship of Slaanesh.",
  "The Thyrrus were a highly mobile, nomadic Xenos species known for their use of sound-based weaponry, now mostly destroyed by the Imperium.",
