  "The Sslyth are massive, serpentine Xenos who serve as mercenaries and bodyguards, often employed by the wealthiest Dark Eldar Archons.",
  "The Grox are massive, domesticated reptilian creatures, widely farmed across the Imperium for their tough, nutritious meat.",
  "The Catachan Jungle Fighters are among the most fearsome Astra Militarum regiments, raised on a death world famous for its monstrous flora and fauna.",
  "The Death Korp of Krieg are grim, suicidal Guardsmen who seek atonement through constant, self-sacrificial warfare.",
  "The Vostroyan Firstborn are an aristocratic, proud Astra Militarum regiment known for their ornate uniforms and heirloom weaponry.",
