  "Cataract of Hate is the name of a massive, long-running Warp Storm that makes travel impossible in a key part of the galaxy.",
  "Promethium is the Imperium's universal fuel, a crude oil derivative often burned for power and used in flamers.",
  "Archetypal Worlds include Forge Worlds, Hive Worlds, Death Worlds, Shrine Worlds, and Agripinaa Worlds (farms).",
