  "The Red Path is the philosophical code of the Khorne Berzerkers, advocating for total, unrestrained bloodletting in all conflicts.",
  "The Great Devourer is the term the Imperium uses to refer to the Tyranid race as a whole, reflecting their terrifying, all-consuming nature.",
  "Infralights are specialized, red-spectrum lights used in Dark Eldar ships to minimize the ambient light and maximize terror.",
  "The Path of the Warrior is the path of life chosen by the Eldar Aspect Warriors, where they temporarily give over their personality to the war mask.",
  "The Codex Astartes includes detailed instructions on Chapter organization, combat doctrine, and even proper color schemes for vehicles.",
  "The Warp Gate is the colloquial term for a stable, permanent portal between the real world and the Immaterium.",
