  "Tomb Kings of Khemri are referenced in ancient Mechanicus texts as another race of deathless, metal-clad warriors.",
  "Star Forts are gigantic, permanent Imperial space stations, serving as command centers, repair docks, and defensive bulwarks.",
  "The Emperor's Champion is a Black Templar selected by divine inspiration to carry a sacred sword and challenge the greatest enemy champion.",
  "The Eightbound are World Eaters possessing eight daemons in a single body.",
  "Corrupted Gene-Seed is the biggest fear of the Apothecaries, as it threatens the purity and future of their entire Chapter.",
  "Hobbyists are a faction of Dark Eldar Haemonculi who experiment on living flesh to create new forms of pain-beasts.",
  "Homunculi are the insane, twisted flesh-sculptors of the Dark Eldar, experts in torture, agony, and biological warfare.",
  "The Red Gobbo is a legendary, revolutionary Ork figure who believes Orks should fight for the small guy (Gretchin), not the big Bosses.",
  "The Green Tide is the colloquial term for a massive, unstoppable Ork WAAAGH! that washes over entire star systems.",
  "The Shas'O is the highest military rank available to a Fire Caste T'au commander.",
  "Markerlights are the T'au's most crucial targeting aids, used to designate enemy targets and increase the accuracy of all subsequent T'au fire.",
