  "Trazyn the Infinite is a notorious Necron Overlord who collects entire populations, buildings, and battlefields, storing them in vast stasis museums.",
  "The Tomb World of Somonor is rumored to contain a working, intact STC blueprint for a powerful new weapon.",
  "The Shadow Captain is the equivalent of a Company Captain in the Raven Guard, specializing in stealth and guerrilla tactics. ",
