  "Tau Drones are ubiquitous robotic assets, serving as mobile shields, weapon platforms, or dedicated field repair systems.",
  "The Vespid Crystal is a unique energy source used by the Vespid Stingwings, which powers their potent ion weaponry.",
  "The Tyrant Guard are massive, heavily armored Tyranid bodyguards, instinctively sacrificing themselves to protect their Hive Tyrant leader.",
  "The Termagants are the basic, fast-moving cannon fodder of the Tyranid swarm, armed with bio-engineered flesh-weapons.",
  "The Exocrine is a massive Tyranid artillery organism, capable of launching powerful salvos of high-explosive bio-projectiles.",
  "The Void Dragon is a C'tan Shard rumored to be imprisoned beneath the surface of Mars, influencing the Machine God's worship.",
  "The Phosphex is a terrifying, ancient, self-igniting chemical weapon used primarily by the Iron Warriors during the Heresy.",
  "The War Boss is the title for the most powerful, battle-crazed Ork commander in a specific region of a WAAAGH!",
  "The Imperial Truth was the Emperor's original, atheistic decree during the Great Crusade, stating that there were no gods, only science and logic.",
  "The Adeptus Administratum has entire sectors of its organization dedicated solely to the documentation and cataloging of other documentation.",
  "The Relic Malice is a heretical Chaos artifact that drives any who touch it into a state of uncontrollable, violent paranoia.",
  "Fulgrim, Primarch of the Emperor's Children, personally slew his brother Ferrus Manus and offered his head to Slaanesh.",
  "The Planet Eater is a term for a massive, ancient Necron weapon capable of destroying entire planetary cores.",
  "Sanctioned Psykers of the Imperium are often fitted with specialized, ornate headwear to help contain and focus their Warp powers.",
