  "A Rogue Trader's power is theoretically absolute within the bounds of their charter, making them minor, private warlords.",
  "The Great Slaughter is the eventual destiny of those who worship Khorne, who will inevitably turn their blades on each other.",
  "The Gellar Field must be disengaged for a ship to drop out of the Warp, making this moment terrifyingly vulnerable.",
  "The Eightbound are World Eaters possessing eight daemons in a single body.",
