  "The Administratum processes millions of logistical requests per second, of which only a tiny fraction are ever correctly actioned.",
  "The Planet of the Sorcerers contains the fortress-pyramid of the Thousand Sons, constantly shifting and defying reality.",
  "The Space Wolves' home world, Fenris, is a highly volatile death world of extreme seismic and volcanic activity.",
  "Terra's surface is coated in centuries of human debris, with the original continents now buried miles deep.",
  "The Golden Throne's daily power drain is so immense that any disruption could plunge the entire Segmentum Solar into darkness.",
  "The Vindicare Assassin's primary weapon is the Exitus Rifle, a silent, high-caliber sniper rifle firing armor-piercing rounds.",
  "The Callidus Assassin's transformation is so total that even medical scans cannot distinguish her from the person she is impersonating.",
